<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to EduHub Academy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .feature-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .feature-item:before {
            content: "✓";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to EduHub Academy!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>

        <p>Welcome to EduHub Academy! We're excited to have you join our learning community.</p>

        <div class="features">
            <h3>What you can do:</h3>
            <div class="feature-item">Access course materials and lecture videos</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Submit assignments and track your progress</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Participate in live classes and discussions</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Receive notifications about important updates</div>
        </div>

        <p>Your account has been successfully created with the email: <strong>{{userEmail}}</strong></p>

        <p>Get started by exploring your dashboard and enrolling in your first course!</p>

        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 EduHub Academy. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at support@eduhub.academy</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
